Key Match Events: Dallas Mavericks won the game 110-93 against the San Antonio Spurs, snapping a four-game losing streak.
Luka Dončić had 16 points on 16 shots, six rebounds, and six assists.
Post-Match Reflections: Luka Dončić admitted he is not 100 percent healthy and promised he will get better.
The win elevated the Dallas Mavericks to a 6-7 record and restored some desperately needed vibes.
